# Codex Handoff — Downlink QoS Implementation

## 完成状态

下行 QoS v1 的 6 个阶段全部完成（阶段 7 dynacast 按计划不进入 v1）。

### 阶段 1：Consumer 控制接口 ✅
- Consumer.h/cpp: 加了 preferredSpatialLayer_, preferredTemporalLayer_, priority_ 字段 + toJson
- RoomService.h/cpp: 加了 pauseConsumer, resumeConsumer, setConsumerPreferredLayers, setConsumerPriority, requestConsumerKeyFrame
- SignalingServer.cpp: 加了 5 个 signaling method 路由
- test_integration.cpp: 3 个集成测试通过

### 阶段 2：浏览器黑盒验证 ✅
- tests/qos_harness/browser/downlink-controls-entry.js
- tests/qos_harness/browser_downlink_controls.mjs
- 3 个 browser case 通过 (pause/resume/keyframe)

### 阶段 3：downlink snapshot schema 与服务端存储 ✅
- src/qos/DownlinkQosTypes.h: DownlinkSubscription, DownlinkSnapshot
- src/qos/DownlinkQosRegistry.h/cpp: 存储 + seq 校验
- QosValidator: ParseDownlinkSnapshot
- RoomService: setDownlinkClientStats
- SignalingServer: downlinkClientStats 路由
- test_qos_integration.cpp: 3 个测试通过

### 阶段 4：最小 downlink QoS v1 ✅
- src/qos/DownlinkAllocator.h/cpp: 3 条规则 (hidden→pause, small→low layer, large/pinned→high layer)
- src/qos/SubscriberQosController.h/cpp: 执行 actions
- RoomService: 接入 allocator
- test_downlink_allocator.cpp: 9 个单测通过
- test_qos_integration.cpp: 3 个集成测试通过

### 阶段 5：健康度驱动的降档与恢复 ✅
- src/qos/DownlinkHealthMonitor.h/cpp: 状态机 (stable/early_warning/congested/recovering)
- DownlinkAllocator: degradeLevel 参数，clamp layers
- test_downlink_health.cpp: 5 个单测通过

### 阶段 6：优先级与房间级分配 ✅
- DownlinkAllocator: ComputePriority, kSetPriority action
- SubscriberQosController: 执行 setPriority
- 优先级模型: screenshare(255) > pinned(220) > activeSpeaker(180) > visible(120) > hidden(0)
- test_downlink_allocator.cpp: 更新为 9 个测试含优先级验证

## 测试汇总
- 14 个 downlink 单测全部通过
- 20 个 integration 测试全部通过
- 6 个 downlink QoS 集成测试全部通过
- browser harness 3 个 case 全部通过

